data.40417046-0341-11eb-9978-02e99e44e93e: This nest is very close to the road and will therefore be disturbed continuously by the traffic on west wise road.  The birds will likely seek refuge in the lush riparian corridor of Coon Creek.

data.cd7dac4e-3be1-11eb-8a94-acde48001122: Two biologists spent about 1 hour looking around with binoculars by hiking along the top of the ridge along the apartments looking down into the grove and then by walking along the creek under the grove. No fliers or sunning.
